    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU1 (CPB hemolysis prediction, Class II, MRL 2) is accepted. All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The six non-assessed factors are consistent with the MRL 2 credibility assessment plan and do not require independent assessment at this risk level. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the subject centrifugal blood pump device.",
